sub_title: Banking professional specialized in Marketing, Consumer Credit and Deposit Products
summary: As a Marketing Manager and Consumer Credit Manager at one of the major banks in Mexico, I learned the importance of building high-quality relationships with customers to drive growth for the organization and my experience working in various areas of the institution gave me a deep understanding of the importance of connecting with customers on a personal level.
